# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:23
msgid "Learn More"
msgstr "Aprender más"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:24
msgid ""
"We are working hard to expand this user guide and to improve OpenShot Video "
"Editor, but if you are stuck and don't know where to turn, OpenShot has "
"several sources for additional information."
msgstr ""
"Estamos trabajando arduamente para ampliar esta guía del usuario y mejorar "
"OpenShot Video Editor, pero si estás atascado y no sabes a dónde acudir, "
"OpenShot tiene varias fuentes de información adicional."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:27
msgid ""
"OpenShot has several `YouTube Tutorials <https://www.youtube.com/playlist?"
"list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_ available to help you learn more."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot tiene varios `Tutoriales en YouTube <https://www.youtube.com/"
"playlist?list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_ disponibles para "
"ayudarte a aprender más."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:28
msgid ""
"OpenShot has a `Reddit User Community <https://openshot.org/forum>`_ "
"dedicated to users helping users, answering questions, and discussing video "
"editing and OpenShot topics."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot tiene una `Comunidad de usuarios en Reddit <https://openshot.org/"
"forum>`_ dedicada a que los usuarios se ayuden entre sí, respondan preguntas "
"y discutan temas de edición de video y OpenShot."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:29
msgid ""
"If you would like to help improve this User Guide, `view source on GitHub "
"<https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tree/develop/doc>`_."
msgstr ""
"Si deseas ayudar a mejorar esta Guía del Usuario, `consulta el código fuente "
"en GitHub <https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tree/develop/doc>`_."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:30
msgid ""
"If you have discovered a new bug, please `Report a Bug <https://www.openshot."
"org/issues/new/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Si has descubierto un error nuevo, por favor `Reporta un error <https://www."
"openshot.org/issues/new/>`_."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:31
msgid ""
"If you need professional support, you can open a ticket by sending an "
"message to support@openshot.org or `Schedule a call <https://calendly.com/"
"openshot-support/desktop>`_."
msgstr ""
"Si necesitas soporte profesional, puedes abrir un ticket enviando un mensaje "
"a support@openshot.org o `programar una llamada <https://calendly.com/"
"openshot-support/desktop>`_."
